to grow two million pounds of food each year,

00:02:05.159 --> 00:02:06.159
without soil.

00:02:06.159 --> 00:02:11.840
The farm will use colored LEDS and nutrient-rich
liquid solutions to grow leafy greens as well

00:02:11.840 --> 00:02:16.340
as herbs and spices, and represents a huge
step in urban farming.

